{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773433287435,"sessionID":"ses_31723c351ffe6G54611rxN573V","part":{"id":"prt_ce8dc6b45001eql1ZIxhOd8DJQ","sessionID":"ses_31723c351ffe6G54611rxN573V","messageID":"msg_ce8dc5f90001YlxGKCoodB1auR","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_011qwo9hVGyrUYm6aftBKreg","tool":"grep","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"tasks.*check|check.*output|parseOutput|output.*flag","include":"*.ts","path":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src"},"output":"Found 13 matches\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/lib/schema.ts:\n  Line 11:  * tasks check` should eventually catch it.\n  Line 397:         name: \"tasks check\",\n\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/lib/output.ts:\n  Line 28:  *   1. Explicit --output flag value\n\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/lib/merger.ts:\n  Line 122:         error: `Failed to checkout ${baseBranch}: ${checkout.output}`,\n\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/index.ts:\n  Line 31:  *   woco tasks check                                  (alias: t ch)\n  Line 101: import { cmdTasksCheck } from \"./commands/tasks/check.js\";\n  Line 417:   tasks check                    (ch)    Validate tasks file (schema, deps, duplicates, cycles)\n  Line 490:   woco tasks check\n\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/commands/tasks/check.ts:\n  Line 2:  * tasks/check.ts — Validate the tasks file for schema issues, broken deps, and orphans.\n  Line 5:  *   woco tasks check\n\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-json-features-check/src/commands/completion.ts:\n  Line 445:     complete -c $cmd -n '__woco_needs_tasks_subcmd' -a 'check'          -d 'Validate tasks'\n  Line 446:     complete -c $cmd -n '__woco_needs_tasks_subcmd' -a 'ch'             -d '→ check'\n  Line 447:     complete -c $cmd -n '__woco_needs_tasks_subcmd' -a 'validate'       -d '→ check'","title":"tasks.*check|check.*output|parseOutput|output.*flag","metadata":{"matches":13,"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773433287332,"end":1773433287412}}}}
