{"type":"text","timestamp":1773433415808,"sessionID":"ses_31723c351ffe6G54611rxN573V","part":{"id":"prt_ce8de4cb3001tj6EdVmtZ1COSo","sessionID":"ses_31723c351ffe6G54611rxN573V","messageID":"msg_ce8de3e9e001gvRWTWU3iLMsyF","type":"text","text":"The implementation is complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### `src/commands/tasks/check.ts`\n1. **Added import** of `output` and `OutputFormat` from `../../lib/output.js`\n2. **Added `outputFmt?: OutputFormat`** to `TasksCheckOptions` interface\n3. **Refactored `cmdTasksCheck`** to:\n   - Resolve format from `opts.outputFmt` (defaulting to `\"text\"`)\n   - Build a structured `issues` array with `{level: \"error\"|\"warning\", message: string}` objects\n   - Compute `ok: boolean` (true when no errors)\n   - Use `output()` helper to emit either JSON `{ok, issues, items_checked}` or the original human-readable text with ANSI codes\n\n### `src/index.ts`\n- Updated the `\"check\"` case in `handleTasksSubcommand` to pass `outputFmt: args.outputFmt` to `cmdTasksCheck`\n\n### `src/lib/schema.ts`\n- Added `--output` flag definition to the `tasks check` command schema (for `woco describe` and shell completions)\n\n### JSON output structure\nWhen invoked with `--output json`, the command emits:\n```json\n{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"issues\": [],\n  \"items_checked\": 42\n}\n```\nOr with issues:\n```json\n{\n  \"ok\": false,\n  \"issues\": [\n    {\"level\": \"error\", \"message\": \"Duplicate ID: \\\"foo\\\"\"},\n    {\"level\": \"warning\", \"message\": \"[bar] No effort estimate\"}\n  ],\n  \"items_checked\": 42\n}\n```","time":{"start":1773433415805,"end":1773433415805}}}
